\f8\fs28 \cb13 chapter_id
\f0\fs32 \cb7  + 
\f8\fs28 \cb13 slot_id
\f0\fs32 \cb7  = same variant index\
- Returns integer 0-4 (not variant name)\
- No external dependencies\
- No randomness\
- No style balancing\
- No arc filtering\
